        <div class="row project-row" data-link="http://howdoispeak.com">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <a href="http://howdoispeak.com" target="_blank">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/static/img/exes2.png" alt="">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <h3><a class="project-title" href="http://howdoispeak.com" target="_blank">HowDoISpeak</a></h3>

                <p>HowDoISpeak is a website that shows
                    you insights about the way you text by analyzing your word choice in your text messages over time.</p>
                <p>
                    The example line graph shows how frequently an anonymous user texted the names of their three exes over time
                    (they all consented to me including this graph).
                </p>
                <p>
                    You can see an anonymous volunteer's full analysis here: <a href="http://howdoispeak.com/sample/">http://howdoispeak.com/sample/</a>
                </p>

                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://howdoispeak.com" target="_blank">View Project <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>

                <p class="author">
                    HowDoISpeak was created in 10/14 by Max Fowler
                </p>
            </div>
