        <!-- Project Two -->
        <div class="row project-row" data-link="http://abridgedmaps.com">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <a href="http://abridgedmaps.com" target="_blank">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="/static/img/rome.png" alt="">
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-5">
                <h3><a class="project-title" href="http://abridgedmaps.com" target="_blank">AbridgedMaps</a></h3>
                <p>Abridged Maps is a website that strips Google Maps of all natural and graphical
                    imagery to reveal concrete poems about the structure of contemporary space.</p>
                <p>We also created a Twitter bot that randomly selects coordinates from a list of
                    3000 cities around the globe and then tweets screen-shots of the Abridged Maps
                    of those locations: <a href="http://twitter.com/abridgedmaps/" target="_blank">@abridgedmaps</a></p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="http://abridgedmaps.com" target="_blank">View Project <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>
                <p class="author">
                    AbridgedMaps was created in 11/15 by Max Fowler and <a href="http://jordibeard.com">Jordan Beard</a>
                </p>
            </div>
