                <h3>LoveGov</h3>
                <p>
                    LoveGov is a non-partisan political social network that crowd-sources political information and connects like-minded people.
                </p>
                <p>
                    All of the company's assets were sold in March of 2013 and the website is no longer active. The 1 minute video linked
                    below shows clips of the original product and describes the company's intention.
                </p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://vimeo.com/48815262" target="_blank">View Project <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>
